    <p>Think of it like washing a frying pan before yesterday's grease hardens. Leave coffee oils sitting too long and they turn nasty fast. Once that happens, even great beans can taste flat and muddy.</p>
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="what-youll-need">
